headline: Conagra Brands Brings Diverse Collection of Snacks to 2025 Sweets & Snacks Expo
summary: Conagra Brands, Inc. (NYSE: CAG), one of North America's leading branded food companies, is preparing to showcase the company's dynamic range of snacks at the National Confectioners Association's 2025 Sweets & Snacks Expo in Indianapolis. Meat snacks, sweet treats, and salty snacks comprise the company's $3.2 billion1 snacks portfolio, with numerous industry-leading brands headlining Conagra Brands' Expo presence.
